pull_request.body:
This new sink API should simplify tests a lot more.

## Before

```js
tape('do my thing', async (t) => {
  await new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
    pull(
      pull.values([10, 20, 30]),
      pull.collect((err, ary) => {
        if (err) reject(err)
        else resolve(ary)
      })
    )
  })
})
```

## After

```js
tape('do my thing', async (t) => {
  const ary = await pull(
    pull.values([10, 20, 30]),
    pull.collectAsPromise()
  })
})
```

